<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink406">
<l>māta ruṇkaṇ makaṉviḷai yāṭak</l>
<l>kātalit taḻīi yiṉitirun taṉaṉē</l>
<l>tātār piraca mūtum</l>
<l>pōtār puṟavi ṉāṭukiḻa vōṉē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
  <l>As [their] son with the beautiful kohl-lined eyes played,</l>
<l>he embraced his beloved and sat [there] sweetly</l>
<l>- [that] lord of the woodland full of flowers</l>
<l>around which bees buzz, growing full on [their] honey.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
